Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Immaculate office and near new warehouse

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
A grade building for lease. Located in the industrial precinct of Smeaton Grange in close proximity to the M5/M7 Motorways and Camden Valley way. This secure building is perfect for a tenant seeking a building in the South West.

> Warehouse Area: 1,316sqm (approx.)
> Office Area: 328sqm (approx.)

* 6 Strata units + 2 Freehold units
* Total building area: 27,331sqm (approx.)
* Total land area: 57,088sqm (approx.)
* Current net income: $2,580,327
* 10 metre+ internal clearance, excellent presentation
* Close proximity to M5 Motorway
* Strong WALE with staggered lease expires

EOI Closing: Tuesday 26th March 2013 at 4.00pm

For further information, or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive agents today.

This prime industrial facility is ideally located on the corner on Orielton Road and Smeaton Grange Road with exposure to the Camden Bypass. Zoned Industrial 4(a) the property is complete with;

- Excellent Yard & Ample Parking

- Container Height Roller Shutters

- High Clearance Warehouse

- Clearspan Showroom with glass frontage

- Wash Bay

Suitable for a wide variety of uses the property can be split in 3 tenancies from 1,021m2 - 7,624m2. Realistic Rental, INSPECTION IS A MUST!

For further information contact Frank Oliveri on 0419 018 356 or Emilios Michael on 0419 014 197
